{"about_the_game":"Underworld Idle is an idle game about underworld management.<br><br>The basic mechanics: higher-order units create lower-order units. If you've played games like Swarm Simulator or Antimatter Dimensions, you should be familiar with these mechanics. However, in Underworld Idle I present my own take on these mechanics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Factions (demons, undead, utopians, and blackseekers). Each faction is responsible for producing its own resource. <br></li><li>Mechanics of creating units. For example, higher demons create lower demons, and so on. The same about units of undead, drowners and warlocks.<br></li><li>Infinite progression. Start with a small number of resources and expand into a long list of units and huge numbers.<br></li><li>Infernal Contracts - Prestige Mechanics.<br></li><li>A variety of locations: lab with energy crystals, junkyard, library with grimoire (containing dark spells).</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Crystal 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1540960/78e9e6ef654223aef07a745b0f43c8669d693336.jpg"},{"name":"Crystal 2","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1540960/ab342f0cbef3bbb1b108663436dd63cf4f76b691.jpg"},{"name":"Crystal 3","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1540960/b1b9405ec0949fa84388fe27fdc6de7e3a546c09.jpg"},{"name":"Crystal 4","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1540960/584d23ea0082e18c9c920e8b305bf97ebb2e3512.jpg"},{"name":"Crystal 5","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1540960/2dff3fff6baf83b7d3155a6fa9cd19178adb03df.jpg"},{"name":"Boiler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1540960/033954559d59f95d63d241a1c604f9ca43a64688.jpg"},{"name":"Obelisk","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/p